values:
Sorry there have been no updates recently, as I have been laid up. Am recovering slowly and hope to get back in the swing of things soon.

For now, a quick note from Coach Leblanc about the team name and a change...

"My owner here at Quabaug, noticed that I had given you the wrong spelling for Armortreds.
It is spelled A-r-m-o-r-t-r-e-d.I had taken the spelling that I gave you off of some reports I have here, but they must have been wrong." 

This will be corrected in the next article. Thanks and TTYL
